		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Super Mario Bros. is incredibly common and has an 8 KiB CHR ROM. It is shipped on the NROM-256 board.
<br />
<br />Super Mario Bros. and Duck Hunt is also incredibly common and has a 16 KiB CHR ROM. It is shipped on a GNROM-compatible board.

		

		</td>
