		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />So what's the difference between VROM and CHR-ROM?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
